    <domain>rag-engineer</domain>
    <summary>RAG pipeline ingests documents, retrieves chunks, generates answers with citations. Use LlamaIndex, Qdrant, reranking. Key: chunk quality bounds retrieval, hybrid search default, MRR > 0.7.</summary>
    <category>rag</category>
